comments: Thornwell (LAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Allen (UTA) after the release and does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Niang (UTA) makes contact with Wallace's (LAC) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Niang (UTA) does not extend his arm into Robinson (LAC) and dislodge him from his defensive position, as his momentum carries him backwards.
Cavanaugh (UTA) and Green (LAC) briefly engage and separate in the post.
Cavanaugh (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Green's (LAC) shot attempt in the post.
Zubac (LAC) sets the screen on Mitrou-Long (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Mitrou-Long (UTA) makes contact with Robinson's (LAC) lower body and affects his ability to land safely following his jump shot attempt.
Bradley (UTA) and Zubac (LAC) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Green (LAC) moves laterally into Allen (UTA) and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Zubac (LAC) sets the screen on Mitrou-Long (UTA) and does not deliver contact.
Zubac (LAC) and Mitrou-Long (UTA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Mitrou-Long (UTA) is still moving laterally into Thronwell's (LAC) path when contact occurs that affects his driving shot attempt.
Robinson (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Allen (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
The Jazz are awarded a timeout while Allen (UTA) is in possession of the ball.
Cavanaugh (UTA) dislodges Robinson (LAC) from his defensive position during the inbound.
Wallace (LAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Niang (UTA) after the release and does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Thornwell (LAC) takes a dribble before the Clippers are awarded the timeout and the Clippers cannot advance the ball following the timeout.
